//////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////*/

/// @notice Calculates the arithmetic average of x and y using the following formula:
///
/// $$
/// avg(x, y) = (x & y) + ((xUint ^ yUint) / 2)
/// $$
///
/// In English, this is what this formula does:
